\title{Charge-spin correlation in van der Waals antiferromagenet $\mathrm{NiPS}_{3}$ }


\author{So Yeun Kim, ${ }^{1,2}$ Tae Yun Kim,,$^{2,3}$ Luke J. Sandilands, ${ }^{1,2}$ Soobin Sinn, ${ }^{1,2}$ Min-Cheol Lee, ${ }^{1,2}$\\
